    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for a daily driver. Mechanically, the engine starts up without issue and the transmission shifts through gears, though you should expect the typical wear and tear that comes with its age. There are some visible scuffs on the exterior and the interior shows signs of regular use, but all major systems are currently operational. It\u2019s a solid, functional car for someone who prioritizes utility over a perfect aesthetic.",
