    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is, ideal for someone looking for a major project or a source for parts. It currently suffers from significant mechanical problems, including a persistent engine knock and a transmission that slips badly when shifting into third gear. The exterior shows its age with extensive rust along the rocker panels and faded paint, while the interior has several tears in the upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. Please be aware that it will likely need to be towed and requires immediate professional attention before it can be driven safely.",
